/*
 
 object consists of 
 
 For ex: Dog object
 state :  breed
 behaviour/attributes : bark,run
 identity:  name of dog
 
 We cant create objects of an abstract class and interface
 * */

/*
 4 Ways To create object
 
   1. object obj = new object();
   2. class.forname [reflection api]
   test obj = test1.class.forname(pkgName).newinstance();
    
   3. clone object
    Object obj = new Object();
    Object obj2 = (Object)obj.clone
   
   4. Deserialization 
    FileInputStream file = new FileInputStream(filename);
	ObjectInputStream in = new ObjectInputStream(file);
	Object obj = in.readObject();


*/
